{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":952,"text":"Today I'm here, actually,\nto pose you a question."},{"time":4056,"text":"What is life?"},{"time":5740,"text":"It has been really puzzling me\nfor more than 25 years,"},{"time":9427,"text":"and will probably continue doing so\nfor the next 25 years."},{"time":13774,"text":"This is the thesis I did\nwhen I was still in undergraduate school."},{"time":19435,"text":"While my colleagues still treated\ncomputers as big calculators,"},{"time":26401,"text":"I started to teach computers to learn."},{"time":29561,"text":"I built digital lady beetles"},{"time":32968,"text":"and tried to learn from real lady beetles,\njust to do one thing:"},{"time":37579,"text":"search for food."},{"time":39321,"text":"And after very simple neural network --"},{"time":42119,"text":"genetic algorithms and so on --"},{"time":44414,"text":"look at the pattern."},{"time":45795,"text":"They're almost identical to real life."},{"time":49977,"text":"A very striking learning experience\nfor a twenty-year-old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55603,"text":"Life is a learning program."},{"time":60259,"text":"When you look\nat all of this wonderful world,"},{"time":63816,"text":"every species has\nits own learning program."},{"time":67585,"text":"The learning program is genome,"},{"time":70370,"text":"and the code of that program is DNA."},{"time":75157,"text":"The different genomes of each species\nrepresent different survival strategies."},{"time":81618,"text":"They represent hundreds of millions\nof years of evolution."},{"time":86879,"text":"The interaction between\nevery species' ancestor"},{"time":90695,"text":"and the environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94150,"text":"I was really fascinated about the world,"},{"time":96613,"text":"about the DNA,"},{"time":97819,"text":"about, you know, the language of life,"},{"time":100786,"text":"the program of learning."},{"time":102767,"text":"So I decided to co-found\nthe institute to read them."},{"time":107524,"text":"I read many of them."},{"time":109589,"text":"We probably read more than half\nof the prior animal genomes in the world."},{"time":114315,"text":"I mean, up to date."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117443,"text":"We did learn a lot."},{"time":119297,"text":"We did sequence, also,\none species many, many times ..."},{"time":123189,"text":"human genome."},{"time":124372,"text":"We sequenced the first Asian."},{"time":126158,"text":"I sequenced it myself many, many times,"},{"time":129020,"text":"just to take advantage of that platform."},{"time":132968,"text":"Look at all those repeating base pairs:"},{"time":135898,"text":"ATCG."},{"time":137390,"text":"You don't understand anything there."},{"time":139328,"text":"But look at that one base pair."},{"time":140946,"text":"Those five letters, the AGGAA."},{"time":143884,"text":"These five SNPs represent\na very specific haplotype"},{"time":147385,"text":"in the Tibetan population"},{"time":149250,"text":"around the gene called EPAS1."},{"time":151273,"text":"That gene has been proved --"},{"time":153028,"text":"it's highly selective --"},{"time":154315,"text":"it's the most significant signature\nof positive selection of Tibetans"},{"time":158686,"text":"for the higher altitude adaptation."},{"time":161102,"text":"You know what?"},{"time":162340,"text":"These five SNPs were the result\nof integration of Denisovans,"},{"time":168151,"text":"or Denisovan-like individuals into humans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172229,"text":"This is the reason\nwhy we need to read those genomes."},{"time":174784,"text":"To understand history,"},{"time":176189,"text":"to understand what kind\nof learning process"},{"time":180311,"text":"the genome has been through\nfor the millions of years."},{"time":185498,"text":"By reading a genome,\nit can give you a lot of information --"},{"time":188445,"text":"tells you the bugs in the genome --"},{"time":190142,"text":"I mean, birth defects,\nmonogenetic disorders."},{"time":193346,"text":"Reading a drop of blood"},{"time":194676,"text":"could tell you why you got a fever,"},{"time":196808,"text":"or it tells you which medicine\nand dosage needs to be used"},{"time":199936,"text":"when you're sick, especially for cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203675,"text":"A lot of things could be studied,\nbut look at that:"},{"time":206819,"text":"30 years ago, we were still poor in China."},{"time":211108,"text":"Only .67 percent of the Chinese\nadult population had diabetes."},{"time":215187,"text":"Look at now: 11 percent."},{"time":217877,"text":"Genetics cannot change over 30 years --"},{"time":221029,"text":"only one generation."},{"time":222905,"text":"It must be something different."},{"time":224556,"text":"Diet?"},{"time":225778,"text":"The environment?"},{"time":227552,"text":"Lifestyle?"},{"time":229399,"text":"Even identical twins\ncould develop totally differently."},{"time":235059,"text":"It could be one becomes\nvery obese, the other is not."},{"time":239034,"text":"One develops a cancer\nand the other does not."},{"time":241560,"text":"Not mentioning living\nin a very stressed environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247566,"text":"I moved to Shenzhen 10 years ago ..."},{"time":250185,"text":"for some reason, people may know."},{"time":253969,"text":"If the gene's under stress,"},{"time":255932,"text":"it behaves totally differently."},{"time":258863,"text":"Life is a journey."},{"time":260817,"text":"A gene is just a starting point,"},{"time":263349,"text":"not the end."},{"time":265286,"text":"You have this statistical risk\nof certain diseases when you are born."},{"time":270392,"text":"But every day you make different choices,"},{"time":273979,"text":"and those choices will increase\nor decrease the risk of certain diseases."},{"time":279428,"text":"But do you know\nwhere you are on the curve?"},{"time":282443,"text":"What's the past curve look like?"},{"time":284959,"text":"What kind of decisions\nare you facing every day?"},{"time":287761,"text":"And what kind of decision is the right one"},{"time":290252,"text":"to make your own right curve\nover your life journey?"},{"time":295445,"text":"What's that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297320,"text":"The only thing you cannot change,"},{"time":299313,"text":"you cannot reverse back,"},{"time":301518,"text":"is time."},{"time":302770,"text":"Probably not yet; maybe in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304795,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305929,"text":"Well, you cannot change\nthe decision you've made,"},{"time":308772,"text":"but can we do something there?"},{"time":310643,"text":"Can we actually try to run\nmultiple options on me,"},{"time":315769,"text":"and try to predict right\non the consequence,"},{"time":319352,"text":"and be able to make the right choice?"},{"time":322153,"text":"After all,"},{"time":323349,"text":"we are our choices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326413,"text":"These lady beetles came to me afterwards."},{"time":329642,"text":"25 years ago, I made\nthe digital lady beetles"},{"time":333129,"text":"to try to simulate real lady beetles."},{"time":335503,"text":"Can I make a digital me ..."},{"time":337897,"text":"to simulate me?"},{"time":339955,"text":"I understand the neural\nnetwork could become"},{"time":342540,"text":"much more sophisticated\nand complicated there."},{"time":345650,"text":"Can I make that one,"},{"time":347228,"text":"and try to run multiple options\non that digital me --"},{"time":351134,"text":"to compute that?"},{"time":353025,"text":"Then I could live in different universes,"},{"time":356012,"text":"in parallel, at the same time."},{"time":359148,"text":"Then I would choose\nwhatever is good for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362243,"text":"I probably have the most comprehensive\ndigital me on the planet."},{"time":366109,"text":"I've spent a lot of dollars\non me, on myself."},{"time":369987,"text":"And the digital me told me\nI have a genetic risk of gout"},{"time":375217,"text":"by all of those things there."},{"time":377254,"text":"You need different technology to do that."},{"time":379389,"text":"You need the proteins, genes,"},{"time":380983,"text":"you need metabolized antibodies,"},{"time":383533,"text":"you need to screen all your body"},{"time":386049,"text":"about the bacterias and viruses\ncovering you, or in you."},{"time":389697,"text":"You need to have\nall the smart devices there --"},{"time":392509,"text":"smart cars, smart house, smart tables,"},{"time":395949,"text":"smart watch, smart phone\nto track all of your activities there."},{"time":399302,"text":"The environment is important --"},{"time":400803,"text":"everything's important --"},{"time":402048,"text":"and don't forget the smart toilet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403818,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":404873,"text":"It's such a waste, right?"},{"time":406671,"text":"Every day, so much invaluable information\njust has been flushed into the water."},{"time":412796,"text":"And you need them."},{"time":414056,"text":"You need to measure all of them."},{"time":415604,"text":"You need to be able to measure\neverything around you"},{"time":418251,"text":"and compute them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420113,"text":"And the digital me told me\nI have a genetic defect."},{"time":424797,"text":"I have a very high risk of gout."},{"time":427868,"text":"I don't feel anything now,"},{"time":429489,"text":"I'm still healthy."},{"time":430885,"text":"But look at my uric acid level."},{"time":432410,"text":"It's double the normal range."},{"time":434919,"text":"And the digital me searched\nall the medicine books,"},{"time":437764,"text":"and it tells me, \"OK, you could\ndrink burdock tea\" --"},{"time":441956,"text":"I cannot even pronounce it right --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443678,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444737,"text":"That is from old Chinese wisdom."},{"time":447076,"text":"And I drank that tea for three months."},{"time":449859,"text":"My uric acid has now gone back to normal."},{"time":453118,"text":"I mean, it worked for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454817,"text":"All those thousands of years\nof wisdom worked for me."},{"time":457357,"text":"I was lucky."},{"time":458864,"text":"But I'm probably not lucky for you."},{"time":463189,"text":"All of this existing\nknowledge in the world"},{"time":465378,"text":"cannot possibly be efficient enough\nor personalized enough for yourself."},{"time":471872,"text":"The only way to make\nthat digital me work ..."},{"time":475424,"text":"is to learn from yourself."},{"time":479093,"text":"You have to ask a lot\nof questions about yourself:"},{"time":481521,"text":"\"What if?\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":483218,"text":"I'm being jet-lagged now here."},{"time":485045,"text":"You don't probably see it, but I do."},{"time":488073,"text":"What if I eat less?"},{"time":489889,"text":"When I took metformin,\nsupposedly to live longer?"},{"time":493574,"text":"What if I climb Mt. Everest?"},{"time":494945,"text":"It's not that easy."},{"time":496271,"text":"Or run a marathon?"},{"time":498132,"text":"What if I drink a bottle of mao-tai,"},{"time":500470,"text":"which is a Chinese liquor,"},{"time":501830,"text":"and I get really drunk?"},{"time":503048,"text":"I was doing a video rehearsal last time\nwith the folks here,"},{"time":507501,"text":"when I was drunk,"},{"time":508794,"text":"and I totally delivered\na different speech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510907,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513800,"text":"What if I work less, right?"},{"time":516125,"text":"I have been less stressed, right?"},{"time":518031,"text":"So that probably never happened to me,"},{"time":519865,"text":"I was really stressed every day,"},{"time":521987,"text":"but I hope I could be less stressed."},{"time":524291,"text":"These early studies told us,"},{"time":526494,"text":"even with the same banana,"},{"time":528501,"text":"we have totally different\nglucose-level reactions"},{"time":531512,"text":"over different individuals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532922,"text":"How about me?"},{"time":534416,"text":"What is the right breakfast for me?"},{"time":536438,"text":"I need to do two weeks\nof controlled experiments,"},{"time":539380,"text":"of testing all kinds of different\nfood ingredients on me,"},{"time":543149,"text":"and check my body's reaction."},{"time":545461,"text":"And I don't know\nthe precise nutrition for me,"},{"time":548602,"text":"for myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551193,"text":"Then I wanted to search\nall the Chinese old wisdom"},{"time":555581,"text":"about how I can live longer,\nand healthier."},{"time":558889,"text":"I did it."},{"time":560141,"text":"Some of them are really unachievable."},{"time":562742,"text":"I did this once last October,"},{"time":565631,"text":"by not eating for seven days."},{"time":568149,"text":"I did a fast for seven days\nwith six partners of mine."},{"time":572778,"text":"Look at those people."},{"time":574061,"text":"One smile."},{"time":575236,"text":"You know why he smiled?"},{"time":576411,"text":"He cheated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577602,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":578626,"text":"He drank one cup of coffee at night,"},{"time":581786,"text":"and we caught it from the data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583295,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584364,"text":"We measured everything from the data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586848,"text":"We were able to track them,"},{"time":589086,"text":"and we could really see --"},{"time":590668,"text":"for example, my immune system,"},{"time":592693,"text":"just to give you a little hint there."},{"time":594479,"text":"My immune system changed\ndramatically over 24 hours there."},{"time":599918,"text":"And my antibody regulates my proteins"},{"time":603075,"text":"for that dramatic change."},{"time":604635,"text":"And everybody was doing that."},{"time":606040,"text":"Even if we're essentially\ntotally different at the very beginning."},{"time":609396,"text":"And that probably will be\nan interesting treatment in the future"},{"time":612465,"text":"for cancer and things like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614132,"text":"It becomes very, very interesting."},{"time":616286,"text":"But something you probably\ndon't want to try,"},{"time":619011,"text":"like drinking fecal water\nfrom a healthier individual,"},{"time":622711,"text":"which will make you feel healthier."},{"time":624402,"text":"This is from old Chinese wisdom."},{"time":626141,"text":"Look at that, right?"},{"time":627601,"text":"Like 1,700 years ago,"},{"time":629791,"text":"it's already there, in the book."},{"time":632608,"text":"But I still hate the smell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634237,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":635411,"text":"I want to find out the true way to do it,"},{"time":637841,"text":"maybe find a combination of cocktails\nof bacterias and drink it,"},{"time":642219,"text":"it probably will make me better."},{"time":643767,"text":"So I'm trying to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644982,"text":"Even though I'm trying this hard,"},{"time":648008,"text":"it's so difficult to test out\nall possible conditions."},{"time":653058,"text":"It's not possible to do\nall kinds of experiments at all ..."},{"time":659341,"text":"but we do have seven billion\nlearning programs on this planet."},{"time":663178,"text":"Seven billion."},{"time":664468,"text":"And every program\nis running in different conditions"},{"time":668143,"text":"and doing different experiments."},{"time":669948,"text":"Can we all measure them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":672962,"text":"Seven years ago,\nI wrote an essay in \"Science\""},{"time":676201,"text":"to celebrate the human genome's\n10-year anniversary."},{"time":680175,"text":"I said, \"Sequence yourself,"},{"time":681853,"text":"for one and for all.\""},{"time":683798,"text":"But now I'm going to say,"},{"time":685690,"text":"\"Digitalize yourself for one and for all.\""},{"time":690275,"text":"When we make this digital me\ninto a digital we,"},{"time":695899,"text":"when we try to form an internet of life,"},{"time":699675,"text":"when people can learn from each other,"},{"time":702560,"text":"when people can learn\nfrom their experience,"},{"time":705291,"text":"their data,"},{"time":707046,"text":"when people can really form\na digital me by themselves"},{"time":710671,"text":"and we learn from it,"},{"time":713416,"text":"the digital we will be\ntotally different with a digital me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719172,"text":"But it can only come from the digital me."},{"time":724103,"text":"And this is what I try to propose here."},{"time":728121,"text":"Join me --"},{"time":729944,"text":"become we,"},{"time":731792,"text":"and everybody should build up\ntheir own digital me,"},{"time":736754,"text":"because only by that\nwill you learn more about you,"},{"time":741297,"text":"about me,"},{"time":742745,"text":"about us ..."},{"time":744678,"text":"about the question I just posed\nat the very beginning:"},{"time":748382,"text":"\"What is life?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":750066,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751259,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":757233,"text":"Chris Anderson:\nOne quick question for you."},{"time":760818,"text":"I mean, the work is amazing."},{"time":762816,"text":"I suspect one question people have is,"},{"time":766038,"text":"as we look forward to these amazing\ntechnical possibilities"},{"time":769343,"text":"of personalized medicine,"},{"time":770728,"text":"in the near-term it feels like\nthey're only going to be affordable"},{"time":774055,"text":"for a few people, right?"},{"time":775355,"text":"It costs many dollars to do\nall the sequencing and so forth."},{"time":778889,"text":"Is this going to lead to a kind of,"},{"time":781825,"text":"you know, increasing inequality?"},{"time":784166,"text":"Or do you have this vision\nthat the knowledge that you get"},{"time":788101,"text":"from the pioneers"},{"time":789477,"text":"can actually be\npretty quickly disseminated"},{"time":791597,"text":"to help a broader set of recipients?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795745,"text":"Jun Wang: Well, good question."},{"time":797303,"text":"I'll tell you that seven years ago,\nwhen I co-founded BGI,"},{"time":800878,"text":"and served as the CEO\nof the company there,"},{"time":804307,"text":"the only goal there for me to do"},{"time":806712,"text":"was to drive the sequencing cost down."},{"time":809044,"text":"It started from 100 million dollars\nper human genome."},{"time":811843,"text":"Now, it's a couple hundred dollars\nfor a human genome."},{"time":814458,"text":"The only reason to do it\nis to get more people to benefit from it."},{"time":818378,"text":"So for the digital me,\nit's the same thing."},{"time":820559,"text":"Now, you probably need,"},{"time":822072,"text":"you know, one million dollars\nto digitize a person."},{"time":825801,"text":"I think it has to be 100 dollars."},{"time":827987,"text":"It has to be free for many of those people\nthat urgently need that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832372,"text":"So this is our goal."},{"time":833993,"text":"And it seems that with all\nthis merging of the technology,"},{"time":837440,"text":"I'm thinking that in the very near future,"},{"time":840056,"text":"let's say three to five years,"},{"time":842445,"text":"it will come to reality."},{"time":843951,"text":"And this is the whole idea\nof why I founded iCarbonX,"},{"time":847954,"text":"my second company."},{"time":849197,"text":"It's really trying to get the cost down"},{"time":852089,"text":"to a level where every individual\ncould have the benefit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":855533,"text":"CA: All right, so the dream is not\nelite health services for few,"},{"time":858605,"text":"it's to really try"},{"time":859863,"text":"and actually make overall health care\nmuch more cost effective --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862998,"text":"JW: But we started\nfrom some early adopters,"},{"time":865452,"text":"people believing ideas and so on,"},{"time":867982,"text":"but eventually, it will become\neverybody's benefit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872303,"text":"CA: Well, Jun, I think\nit's got to be true to say"},{"time":874660,"text":"you're one of the most amazing\nscientific minds on the planet,"},{"time":877642,"text":"and it's an honor to have you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879095,"text":"JW: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880277,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}